The paper focuses on natural language processing techniques to extract useful information from security forums. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), cryptography and security (cs.CR), information retrieval (cs.IR), social and information networks (cs.SI), and machine learning (cs.LG).
